1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 15=

3
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:00,300
You're awake.

4
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:02,680
Why aren't you sleeping a little longer?

5
00:01:03,020 --> 00:01:05,820
I was worried you'd be too tired,
so I wanted to make you something to eat.

6
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:09,099
Worried I'd be too tired?

7
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:09,860
Mm.

8
00:01:14,180 --> 00:01:15,780
If you hadn't begged
for mercy last night,

9
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:17,900
would you still
be cooking here right now?

10
00:01:20,060 --> 00:01:21,060
What are you doing?

11
00:01:21,220 --> 00:01:22,300
This is the kitchen.

12
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,140
What's wrong with the kitchen?

13
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,790
Then aren't you going to eat anymore?

14
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:27,940
That's not important.

15
00:01:46,380 --> 00:01:47,340
You are here.

16
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:49,020
Have some fruit.

17
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:51,300
Thank you.

18
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,700
Have you been sleeping here
this whole time?

19
00:01:56,220 --> 00:01:57,420
You've really suffered.

20
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:03,380
What are you doing?

21
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:05,290
I haven't suffered at all.

22
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:16,180
How is it?

23
00:02:16,380 --> 00:02:17,100
Is it sweet?

24
00:02:20,180 --> 00:02:21,380
Want to know?

25
00:02:22,580 --> 00:02:23,580
Try it yourself.

26
00:02:43,220 --> 00:02:44,299
Let's go back to the bedroom.

27
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:45,420
There's no time.

28
00:03:17,380 --> 00:03:18,340
Darling.

29
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:19,500
Darling, it's me.

30
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:21,220
I'm your husband, Gu Nianchi.

31
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:22,819
Did you discover he's fake?

32
00:03:22,820 --> 00:03:24,060
I'm the real Commander.

33
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:26,140
You came to save me,

34
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:27,380
didn't you?

35
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:29,620
Save you?

36
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:32,620
I wish I could tear you to pieces.

37
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:34,500
Gu Shaoyan.

38
00:03:36,940 --> 00:03:38,220
My name is Gu Nianchi,

39
00:03:38,860 --> 00:03:40,020
not Gu Shaoyan.

40
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,620
Have you been working with my brother
behind my back all along?

41
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:49,580
You've both been waiting
for today, haven't you?

42
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,820
He really has always desired you.

43
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:56,580
Desired his own sister in law!

44
00:03:56,660 --> 00:03:57,860
This has nothing to do with him.

45
00:03:58,140 --> 00:03:59,099
Everything I've done,

46
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,380
from the very beginning,

47
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:02,740
was to take your life.

48
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:06,780
Why?

49
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,060
I liked you so much.

50
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:11,020
Back at Paramount,

51
00:04:11,510 --> 00:04:13,060
the way you looked
while playing the piano

52
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,250
was truly beautiful.

53
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:18,340
That was when

54
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:21,100
I fell in love with you at first sight.

55
00:04:22,220 --> 00:04:23,020
That's right.

56
00:04:24,580 --> 00:04:26,260
I even killed Lily myself

57
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:29,060
for bullying you.

58
00:04:29,730 --> 00:04:30,900
Are you happy now?

59
00:04:32,340 --> 00:04:34,380
I was wondering why
no one could find Lily anywhere.

60
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,140
So it was you.

61
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:39,940
Yes, it was me.

62
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,900
I've treated you so well.

63
00:04:43,820 --> 00:04:45,140
Why did you betray me?

64
00:04:46,020 --> 00:04:47,860
Do you really not remember?

65
00:04:48,420 --> 00:04:50,060
Then let me help you remember.

66
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:51,820
Three years ago,

67
00:04:52,350 --> 00:04:53,260
you

68
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:55,100
killed my entire family.

69
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:58,120
You shot me here,

70
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:00,860
made me misunderstand the person
I loved most for three whole years.

71
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:02,940
Do you remember now?

72
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,580
The person you loved most?

73
00:05:07,980 --> 00:05:09,300
Three years?

74
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:20,540
Didn't you once say
you wanted to marry me?

75
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:23,620
What a pity.

76
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:29,499
You're the reason I was separated
from the person I loved most

77
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:31,740
for three whole years.

78
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:35,700
I remember now.

79
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:39,900
You're the daughter of the Zhuang family
from three years ago,

80
00:05:40,940 --> 00:05:41,939
Zhuang Yun...

81
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:43,540
You finally remembered.

82
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:45,100
Gu Shaoyan.

83
00:05:48,740 --> 00:05:50,620
So it really was you.

84
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,460
You carefully plotted your way
into the Commander's Residence.

85
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:56,060
From the very beginning,

86
00:05:56,620 --> 00:05:58,359
you came to kill me, didn't you?

87
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,940
Not just kill you.

88
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:02,140
I want to carve you into pieces.

89
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:03,860
Let me tell you.

90
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:04,940
All these years,

91
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:07,420
not a single moment has passed
without me thinking about

92
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:10,380
how to use your blood
to honor the souls of the Zhuang family.

93
00:06:11,020 --> 00:06:12,740
But I never could have imagined

94
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,100
that you'd be this deceitful.

95
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:16,680
Using Lu Shaoyuan as your stand in.

96
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:19,080
If your Zhuang family hadn't hidden
that shipment of opium back then,

97
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,360
your entire family wouldn't
have been wiped out.

98
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,640
You only brought this upon yourselves.
What does it have to do with me?

99
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,460
Shut up!

100
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:24,979
It was because our Zhuang family

101
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:26,619
refused to join your filthy dealings

102
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:28,300
that you framed us.

103
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:32,220
And even now,
you still refuse to admit your crimes?

104
00:06:35,260 --> 00:06:36,380
What are you trying to do?

105
00:06:38,100 --> 00:06:39,340
Are you going to kill me?

106
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:43,859
My brother won't let you kill me.

107
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:45,900
He'll never agree to it.

108
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:51,779
You really think
he doesn't want you dead?

109
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:53,580
I'm his brother.

110
00:06:53,700 --> 00:06:56,219
You stole his name
and took his place as Commander.

111
00:06:56,220 --> 00:06:58,620
Now you remember you're his brother?

112
00:06:59,740 --> 00:07:00,780
Zhuang Yunqiu,

113
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:03,819
Lu Shaoyuan looks exactly like me.

114
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:06,860
What makes you so certain
that I committed those crimes?

115
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:07,900
You...

116
00:07:08,740 --> 00:07:11,180
You're not even worthy
of being compared to him.

117
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:15,139
Lu Shaoyuan has always carried warmth
and light within him.

118
00:07:15,140 --> 00:07:16,340
And you...

119
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:19,140
You're just a rat
hiding in the darkness.

120
00:07:19,420 --> 00:07:20,780
Your life

121
00:07:21,260 --> 00:07:23,180
will never see the light of day.

122
00:07:23,940 --> 00:07:24,820
Shut up.

123
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:26,420
Shut up!

124
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,459
When you harmed
all those innocent people,

125
00:07:30,460 --> 00:07:32,660
did you ever think
you'd end up like this one day?

126
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:35,740
What do those people's lives or deaths

127
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:38,660
have to do with me?

128
00:07:43,740 --> 00:07:44,579
This stab

129
00:07:44,580 --> 00:07:45,859
is for my father,

130
00:07:45,860 --> 00:07:48,700
and for the fifteen lives
of everyone in the Zhuang family!

131
00:07:49,620 --> 00:07:51,219
Your father sold opium.

132
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:53,140
I executed him in the name of justice!

133
00:07:54,660 --> 00:07:55,379
This stab

134
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:57,180
is for Lu Shaoyuan.

135
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:59,420
You ignored the bond between brothers

136
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:00,339
and broke his heart.

137
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:02,939
I generously offered to share
the Commander's position with him,

138
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:05,499
yet he repaid kindness with betrayal
and stole what belonged to me.

139
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:06,880
The one who deserves to die is him!

140
00:08:07,940 --> 00:08:08,979
The third stab

141
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:11,780
is for the innocent people
of all Yancheng!

142
00:08:27,450 --> 00:08:33,190
♪What is there to seek or desire,
trapped in worldly sorrow?♪

143
00:08:33,770 --> 00:08:39,670
♪Entangled through lifetimes,
drawn into chaos and schemes♪

144
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:43,330
♪Your silhouette♪

145
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:46,170
♪Carved through endless hardship♪

146
00:09:16,780 --> 00:09:17,860
You're awake.

147
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:28,420
How long was I asleep?

148
00:09:28,860 --> 00:09:29,900
A full day and night.

149
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:36,020
I didn't kill him.

150
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:38,340
I know.

151
00:09:41,100 --> 00:09:42,459
He's committed every evil imaginable

152
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:43,780
and lost every shred of conscience.

153
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:47,500
I truly wanted to take his life.

154
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:49,700
But the reason I didn't kill him

155
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:51,940
wasn't because he's your brother.

156
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:54,140
It was because

157
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:57,620
I wanted justice to be upheld
through the fairness of the law.

158
00:09:57,940 --> 00:09:59,419
I want him despised by everyone,

159
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:00,540
repenting every single day.

160
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,620
We're thinking the same thing.

161
00:10:11,820 --> 00:10:13,100
But fortunately,

162
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:15,820
heaven is still fair.

163
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:18,060
You reclaimed your place
as the Commander,

164
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:20,020
and your own name as well.

165
00:10:21,300 --> 00:10:22,580
I don't care about that anymore.

166
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:25,860
The name Gu Nianchi

167
00:10:25,900 --> 00:10:27,700
stopped being my name long ago.

168
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:31,340
Ever since my mother passed away,

169
00:10:32,860 --> 00:10:34,420
I've been called Lu Shaoyuan.

170
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:44,290
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

171
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:50,920
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

172
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:55,000
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

173
00:10:55,340 --> 00:10:58,350
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

174
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:03,640
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

175
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:09,950
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

176
00:11:11,010 --> 00:11:16,610
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

177
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:20,530
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

178
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:23,729
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

179
00:11:23,730 --> 00:11:28,869
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

180
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:33,189
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

181
00:11:33,190 --> 00:11:35,769
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

182
00:11:35,770 --> 00:11:38,049
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

183
00:11:38,050 --> 00:11:41,599
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

184
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:46,129
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

185
00:11:46,130 --> 00:11:48,660
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

186
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:50,749
♪Still I walk into♪

187
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:54,349
♪The trap you set without regret♪

188
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:58,399
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

189
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,979
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

190
00:12:00,980 --> 00:12:03,139
♪A stand in can never cross♪

191
00:12:03,140 --> 00:12:06,579
♪The shortest distance between us♪

192
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:11,550
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

193
00:12:11,710 --> 00:12:16,380
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

194
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,729
♪A substitute♪

195
00:12:20,730 --> 00:12:25,730
♪Needs no reason♪

